{"tid":295801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】黑警起腳踢野豬反失平衡跌倒","createTime":"2017-06-24T04:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T03:04:26.000Z","uid":20933,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4fda265fecf9751ff719b2806e80bd1b0a9192e","tid":295801,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170624/large/1498275859_dacc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170624%2Flarge%2F1498275859_dacc.jpg&h=cb3ed7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170624/large/1498275864_5456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170624%2Flarge%2F1498275864_5456.jpg&h=0af018c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上7時38分，一頭野豬被途人發現在將軍澳日出康城路單車徑出沒，其間更亂竄疑似覓食，一名姓李(74歲)踩單車的老翁見狀停下，惟野豬仍撞向單車，李伯當場人仰車翻，跌在地上，手腳擦傷，野豬繼而再撞另一名姓張(34歲)男途人，張手部擦傷，兩人俱清醒送院。<br />\n<br />\n野豬逞兇後匿在附近草叢，警員接報到場，手持盾牌在附近戒備。至早上10時許，漁護署人員到場，張開圍網罩着草叢，並推來鐵籠展開圍捕。其間約20名警員及漁護署人員將草叢重重包圍，多人持盾牌壓向野豬，但野豬掙扎逃脫，再度衝出單車徑。有警員起腳踢向野豬時，疑因野豬體型龐大，警員反而失平衡跌倒。野豬邁開前蹄及後腿奮力直衝，撞向漁護署車輛的左邊車門，將車門撞凹，復匿至另一端草叢。疑因野豬已乏力，終被在場的警員以盾牌壓著按地制服，交由漁護署人員處理。<br />\n<br />\n被撞傷的李伯在醫院時表示，當時他釣完魚踩單車準備由日出康城返回尚德邨寓所，其間被野豬撞跌，連人帶車跌落地，「我騎單車，佢（野豬）走出嚟，就撞跌我，我從來未見過野豬，有啲驚。」他兩手的手肘、手指及腳均擦傷，他經敷治後返回現場取回單車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170624&amp;guid=56869561&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170624%26guid%3D56869561%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=YKzynfpU1Su0DL7YfLqOpgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4e06e05c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170624%26guid%3D56869561%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=098db96d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170624&amp;guid=56869561&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"7f782a12a1ca6f67bb69b6dde1edce88b7978b95","tid":295801,"uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170624/large/1498275866_47f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170624%2Flarge%2F1498275866_47f5.jpg&h=8545b31f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漁護署的車輛亦被撞凹。(文兆麟攝)"},{"pid":"30951b77196bbe9d5e679624cf9b8e5967ede828","tid":295801,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170624/s00001/71e0875fe40697eebfdcc92302486aaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170624%2Fs00001%2F71e0875fe40697eebfdcc92302486aaa.jpg&h=ffc64e32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"184bf660d2cc3d14a3d286b02737094d124bb674","tid":295801,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170624/s00001/7124c95c9a61a295fb70d114fd826443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170624%2Fs00001%2F7124c95c9a61a295fb70d114fd826443.jpg&h=edf44e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170624/s00001/7121658cb3d86eef2c5fd644946cdb0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170624%2Fs00001%2F7121658cb3d86eef2c5fd644946cdb0b.jpg&h=01973b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170624/s00001/711f7e1f0ac052fb397103711ae5aca7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170624%2Fs00001%2F711f7e1f0ac052fb397103711ae